Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浩平...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直...在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不记得我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还记得你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折原 浩平
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定 会再见的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定 我一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 不要忘了我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远的誓约
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明约好了的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人遗忘...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是件可怕的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你还是要走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 一定会再见的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁弹的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 是谁...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 冰上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长森...同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才拉大提琴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是冰上君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何 有种令人怀念的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是茧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们认识？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校后面的杂木林里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 她最喜欢的雪貂死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正一个人伤心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉的雪貂的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给它修了个坟是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给小米欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 所以每次回想起来都会伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 人才会选择遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的晚霞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它最喜欢的花？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以它一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 茧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先去吧 我随后到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么约定好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉勾勾 说谎的人要吃一千根针
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉勾勾 说谎的人要...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远的...誓约
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎的人要吃一千根针...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他...已经走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经走了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 是你过世妹妹的替身？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻上去好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名 茧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是 折原浩平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘记我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他走了...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说「不要忘记我」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远 是根本不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远 是存在的哦
